= Collaboration Sandbox =
Just click on '''"Show comments"''' below to read and add comments.

Have a look at [[User:Collaboration|the article of our sandbox user]] to discover his latest comments powered by [[Template:Show comments infobox for user]]. Feel free to use this template on all your user pages by entering <pre>
{{Show comments infobox for user
|show=True
}}
</pre> to these articles.

We also created [[Collaboration_best_articles|a sample article to display the best rated articles]] in this wiki that calls [[Template:Show best rated articles]]. You can use this template call in any other pages, too. <pre>
{{Show best rated articles
|show=True
}}
</pre>

More information can be found also in the [http://smwforum.ontoprise.com/smwforum/index.php?title=Help:Using_the_Collaboration_extension_1.3&context=Help%3ACollaboration+extension+1.3 Collaboration extension help article]. Get this extension on our [http://smwforum.ontoprise.com/smwforum/index.php/Download download page]!

